<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Tambola Game Provider</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/_nav') %>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-section text-center py-5 mt-5" style="background: var( --card-gradient);">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="display-4 text-white">Welcome to Host Tambola</h1>
                <p class="lead text-white">Your ultimate platform to create, manage, and play Tambola games with ease.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-lg text-white mt-3" style="background: var(--primary-color);">Get
                    Started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Us Section -->
        <section class="about py-5">
            <div class="container text-center">
                <h2 class="fw-bold" style="color: var(--primary-color);">About Us</h2>
                <p class="lead">We are the leading provider of tambola games, offering a variety of exciting features
                    for players worldwide.</p>
                <p>Our platform is designed to bring the fun of tambola directly to your screen, with a secure and
                    user-friendly interface. Whether you're hosting a virtual event or enjoying a game with friends, we
                    ensure a top-notch experience.</p>
                <p>With real-time updates, secure transactions, and customizable themes, we aim to make your gaming
                    experience enjoyable and memorable. Join thousands of users who trust us to bring their events to
                    life with exciting tambola games!</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Team Section -->
        <section class="middle-section py-5" style="background: var( --card-gradient);">
            <div class="container text-center">
                <h2 class="fw-bold" style="color: var(--primary-color);">Our Team</h2>
                <p>We are a passionate group of software developers based in <mark class="big"
                        style="background-color: var(--secondary-color); color: white;">Kolkata</mark>, West Bengal,
                    India. With a deep love for gaming and technology, our team works tirelessly to create innovative
                    and seamless experiences for our users.</p>
                <p>Our developers and designers work hand-in-hand to ensure that our platform stays secure, scalable,
                    and user-friendly, allowing players to focus on what matters most: the game.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section class="container py-5">
            <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--primary-color);">Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4">

                <!-- Card 1: Easy Setup -->
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card feature-card"
                        style="background: var(--card-gradient); border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); transition: transform 0.3s;">
                        <div class="card-body text-center text-white">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up mb-3" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Easy Setup</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Host your tambola games in minutes with our simple setup process. No
                                technical skills needed.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2: Real-Time Updates -->
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card feature-card"
                        style="background: var(--card-gradient); border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); transition: transform 0.3s;">
                        <div class="card-body text-center text-white">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-clock mb-3" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Real-Time Updates</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Enjoy instant updates on your game with live number calling and
                                automatic winner notifications.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 3: Customization -->
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card feature-card"
                        style="background: var(--card-gradient); border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); transition: transform 0.3s;">
                        <div class="card-body text-center text-white">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-palette mb-3" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Customization</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Customize the look and feel of your games with personalized themes and
                                designs to match your event.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <%- include('partials/_footer') %>

            <!-- Bootstrap JS and dependencies -->
            <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>